1
00:00:00,540 --> 00:00:04,360
Tudi spim, recimo, včasih, ko
plavam, ne, in fantje, recimo, ne,

2
00:00:04,440 --> 00:00:05,380
ko. Čakaj, kako to misliš?

3
00:00:05,460 --> 00:00:06,960
Spim v vodi,

4
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:08,620
ne in plavam. -Ja,
ampak verjetno ne plavaš.

5
00:00:08,700 --> 00:00:10,900
Ja, spim in plavam istočasno,

6
00:00:10,980 --> 00:00:14,440
ja. In recimo, fantje, ko začnem
jaz sem pa kaj it, takoj vejo,

7
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:17,920
da ne. On mora samo pazit,
ko vozi, da me ne povozi motor.

8
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:19,420
Se pravi, tebi, čakaj malo

9
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:20,980
ja, telo ti dela?

10
00:00:21,060 --> 00:00:24,260
Telo mi dela, ampak ti
pa spiš. -Jaz pa spim,
